<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>yạ nfsy qwmy hlly</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- yā naf̊sī qūmī halĩlī
 bisub̊ḥi fādīki ạl̊ʿalī̃̊
 fah̊wa laki rabuⁿ̃ raḥīm̊
 qad̊ fāqa ḥubũhu ạl̊ʿaẓīm̊

[V2]
 2- qad̊ raqã lī rabũ ạlsãmā
 ạản̊qadẖanī mina ạlsẖãqā
 ʿanĩy qaḍay̱ dẖāka ạl̊ḥabīb̊
 qad̊ fāqa ḥubũhu ạl̊ʿajīb̊

[V3]
 3- ại̹dẖā ạb̊tagẖat̊ jun̊du ạl̊ʿiday̱
 ại̹b̊ʿādī ʿan̊ ṭur̊qi ạl̊huday̱
 yah̊dī ṭarīqī fī ạl̊masīr̊
 qad̊ fāqa ḥubũhu ạl̊katẖīr̊

[V4]
 4- ại̹n̊ ạảz̊ʿajat̊ qal̊bī ạl̊humūm̊
 fī ṣaẘti raʿ̊diⁿ kāl̊gẖuyūm̊
 yaj̊lū ṣadā qal̊bī ạl̊katẖīf̊
 qad̊ fāqa ḥubũhu ạllãṭīf̊

[V5]
 5- ại̹n̊ juz̊tu wādī ạl̊maẘti lạ
 ạảkẖ̊sẖay̱ wabālạaⁿ muq̊bilạ
 fālrãbũ lī niʿ̊ma ạl̊muʿīn̊
 qad̊ fāqa ḥubũhu ạltẖãmīn̊

[V6]
 6- yum̊nāhu tah̊dīnī ại̹lay̱
 ại̹r̊tẖiⁿ saʿīdiⁿ fī ạl̊ʿulạ
 fālsẖũk̊ru lil̊fādī ạl̊majīd̊
 qad̊ fāqa ḥubũhu ạlsẖãdīd̊</lyrics>
</song>